&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s Degree is required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous legal services experience or a J.D. a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3 - 5 years’ of relevant account management, relationship management and/or customer relations experience essential.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to develop and secure relationships at all levels within a customer organization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exudes superior business acumen, poise and executive presence. Highly articulate.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deadline-driven with excellent time management and organizational skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong computer skills including knowledge of Salesforce and Microsoft Office.&lt;/li&gt;
